task.summary: Added DataSetObservable to vehicle classes and made a VehicleMap to handle and auto update
Changing vehicle name updates nav drawer automatically
Help memory usage on image load
Initial work moving all primary data management to CarSQL
Changed STRING SQLite columns to TEXT
loading vehicle images only once to cache in CarSql
Memory usage on loading images much much better
Size of image cache is now related to VM memory
Setup LruCache that remove's based on bitmap in cache that was used last
Updated nav drawer header display updating
Menu button UI color change setup fix
Better icons and main fragment style
Initial work on calculating average efficiency
Make units set in by vehicle
Moved to Support Fragments and working on Bitmap caching
Made data save when values were removed
UI for EditCar and initial launch tweaking
Remove MobiHelp and setup to use BitmapCache jCenter library
Added Transaction capability of SQLDataHandler Clean SQLDataHandler put* names

Implement SQLDataHandler transaction in Vehicle and ServiceTask
